title: FS briefs diplomatic missions on developments in IIOJK
content:
ISLAMABAD, Aug 4 (APP):Ahead of ‘Youm-e-Istehsal’ on August 5 , Foreign Secretary Dr Asad Majeed Friday here briefed the Islamabad-based diplomatic missions on the latest developments in Indian Illegally Occupied Jammu and Kashmir (IIOJK).According to Foreign Office, he highlighted the legal, security and human rights dimensions of the situation in IIOJK.
